full_text: to see about it because she worships him * it would just create problems I wouldn't tell Many one else because it is still not a big deal + I didn't want to portray him in a bad light. I really don't think it is a big deal. I think he is just a relaxed guy & likes to put, or was being fatherly or something I know this sounds like me trying to justify him doing something weird but it isn't. I am enjoying, actually am in a pretty good period - This could all be over by tomorrow but I feel pretty happy right now & excited for the future ( not immediate - track & school), this summer (after year, & college.
